---
title: Student Registration — Sequence Diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Student
    participant UI as Frontend
    participant API as Express API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant A as Admin
    participant SC as Smart Contract

    S->>UI: Install MetaMask & get SepoliaETH
    S->>UI: Fill registration form (name, ID, year, gender, photo)
    S->>UI: Submit registration code
    S->>UI: Set account password
    UI->>API: POST /api/student/register
    API->>DB: INSERT student (wallet_verified=false)
    API-->>UI: Registration submitted
    UI-->>S: Status: Awaiting Verification

    A->>UI: Review student details
    A->>API: Approve registration
    API->>DB: UPDATE eligible_to_vote=true
    API->>SC: Submit updated Merkle root
    SC-->>API: MerkleRootUpdated event
    API-->>UI: Student verified
    UI-->>S: Status: Ready to Vote
